Merkezi Sunucu Yapılandırması | Central Server Configuration
Bu script, ağ üzerindeki paylaşılan klasörden verileri toplar, analiz eder ve Microsoft Graph API kullanarak yönetici ekibine raporlar.
This script collects data from the network share, analyzes it, and reports it to the IT administration using Microsoft Graph API.

Central-Server-Script.ps1
Bu script, sunucu tarafında her akşam belirlenen saatte (Örn: 18:00) çalışacak şekilde Task Scheduler üzerinden tetiklenir.
This script is triggered via Task Scheduler on the server side at a set time (e.g., 6:00 PM).

PowerShell
# =====================================================
# 1. AYARLAR | SETTINGS
# =====================================================
# Azure App Registration Bilgileri | Azure App Registration Credentials
$TenantId     = "<YOUR_TENANT_ID>"
$ClientId     = "<YOUR_CLIENT_ID>"
$ClientSecret = "<YOUR_CLIENT_SECRET>"

# Mail Ayarlari | Mail Settings
$MailFrom = "<REPORTS_SENDER_MAIL>"
$MailTo   = @("<RECIPIENT_1>", "<RECIPIENT_2>") 

# Yol Tanimlari | Path Definitions
$SharePath   = "\\<YOUR_SERVER>\<SHARE_NAME>$"
$WorkingPath = "C:\CentralEventReport"
$FinalCsv    = "$WorkingPath\MergedEvents.csv"
$ZipPath     = "$WorkingPath\MergedEvents.zip"

$MinutesBack = 4320 # Son 3 gunu tara | Scan last 3 days

# Olay Aciklamalari (Ihtiyaca gore guncellenebilir) 
# Event Descriptions (Can be updated as needed)
$EventDescriptions = @{
    "7"    = "Disk Hatasi (Bad Block) | Disk Error"
    "11"   = "Surucu Denetleyici Hatasi | Controller Error"
    "51"   = "Disk Yazma Hatasi (Paging Error) | Paging Error"
    "18"   = "Fatal Donanim Hatasi (WHEA) | Fatal Hardware Error"
    "47"   = "Disk Cikarildi | Disk Removed"
    "4101" = "Ekran Surucusu Yanit Vermeyi Kesti | Display Driver Timeout"
    "14"   = "Cihaz Yanit Vermiyor | Device Not Responding"
    "219"  = "Surucu Yukleme Hatasi (Kernel-PnP) | Driver Load Failure"
    "225"  = "Uygulama Kapatma Hatasi | App Shutdown Error"
}

# =====================================================
# 2. VERI TOPLAMA VE ANALIZ | DATA COLLECTION & ANALYSIS
# =====================================================
if (!(Test-Path $WorkingPath)) { New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $WorkingPath | Out-Null }

$CutoffTime = (Get-Date).AddMinutes(-$MinutesBack)
$CsvFiles = Get-ChildItem $SharePath -Filter *.csv | Where-Object { $_.LastWriteTime -ge $CutoffTime }

if (!$CsvFiles) { 
    Write-Host "Yeni veri bulunamadi. | No new data found."
    return 
}

$RawData = New-Object System.Collections.Generic.List[PSObject]

foreach ($File in $CsvFiles) {
    try {
        # CSV temizleme ve veri okuma | CSV cleaning and data reading
        $CleanLines = Get-Content $File.FullName | Where-Object { $_ -match '^"' }
        if ($CleanLines) {
            $Data = $CleanLines | ConvertFrom-Csv -Delimiter ";" 
            $DeviceName = $File.BaseName -replace "Events_",""
            foreach ($Row in $Data) {
                $EventID = if ($Row.Id) { $Row.Id } else { $Row.EventID }
                if ($EventID) {
                    $RawData.Add([PSCustomObject]@{ "DeviceName" = $DeviceName; "EventID" = $EventID.ToString().Trim() })
                }
            }
        }
    } catch { }
}

# Veriyi Cihaz Bazli Grupla | Group Data by Device Name
$GroupedData = $RawData | Group-Object DeviceName | ForEach-Object {
    $UniqueIDs = $_.Group.EventID | Select-Object -Unique
    
    $DescList = foreach ($id in $UniqueIDs) {
        if ($EventDescriptions.ContainsKey($id)) {
            "${id}: $($EventDescriptions[$id])"
        }
    }

    [PSCustomObject]@{
        "Device Name"       = $_.Name
        "Event IDs"         = $UniqueIDs -join ", "
        "Critical Descriptions" = $DescList -join " | "
    }
}

# Raporu disari aktar ve sikistir | Export and compress the report
$GroupedData | Export-Csv -Path $FinalCsv -NoTypeInformation -Encoding UTF8 -Delimiter ","
if (Test-Path $ZipPath) { Remove-Item $ZipPath -Force }
Compress-Archive -Path $FinalCsv -DestinationPath $ZipPath

# =====================================================
# 3. GRAPH API ILE MAIL VE TEMIZLIK | MAIL VIA GRAPH API & CLEANUP
# =====================================================
try {
    # Token Alimi | Get OAuth Token
    $TokenUrl = "https://login.microsoftonline.com/$TenantId/oauth2/v2.0/token"
    $TokenBody = @{ grant_type = "client_credentials"; client_id = $ClientId; client_secret = $ClientSecret; scope = "https://graph.microsoft.com/.default" }
    $TokenResponse = Invoke-RestMethod -Method Post -Uri $TokenUrl -Body $TokenBody
    $Headers = @{ "Authorization" = "Bearer $($TokenResponse.access_token)"; "Content-Type" = "application/json" }
    
    $AttachmentBase64 = [Convert]::ToBase64String([IO.File]::ReadAllBytes($ZipPath))
    $RecipientList = @(); foreach ($Mail in $MailTo) { $RecipientList += @{ emailAddress = @{ address = $Mail } } }

    $MailJson = @{
        message = @{
            subject = "Client Critical Event Analysis Report - $(Get-Date -Format 'dd.MM.yyyy')"
            body = @{ 
                contentType = "HTML"
                content = "<html><body><p>Device-based critical event analysis report is attached.</p><p><b>Total Devices Count:</b> $($GroupedData.Count)</p></body></html>" 
            }
            toRecipients = $RecipientList
            attachments = @(@{ "@odata.type" = "#microsoft.graph.fileAttachment"; name = "Critical_Event_Analysis.zip"; contentBytes = $AttachmentBase64 })
        }
    } | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 10 -Compress

    # Mail Gonder | Send Mail
    Invoke-RestMethod -Method Post -Uri "https://graph.microsoft.com/v1.0/users/$MailFrom/sendMail" -Headers $Headers -Body $MailJson
    
    # --- TEMIZLIK (YEREL + PAYLASIM) | CLEANUP (LOCAL + SHARE) ---
    if (Test-Path $FinalCsv) { Remove-Item $FinalCsv -Force }
    if (Test-Path $ZipPath) { Remove-Item $ZipPath -Force }
    foreach ($File in $CsvFiles) { 
        if (Test-Path $File.FullName) { Remove-Item $File.FullName -Force }
    }
    Write-Host "Success: Process completed and logs cleared." -ForegroundColor Green
} catch { 
    Write-Host "ERROR: $($_.Exception.Message)" -ForegroundColor Red 
}






Teknik Detaylar | Technical Details
Neden Microsoft Graph API?: Geleneksel SMTP yöntemlerine göre daha güvenlidir, Modern Authentication (OAuth 2.0) destekler ve Exchange Online kısıtlamalarına takılmaz. 
Why Microsoft Graph API?:It is more secure than traditional SMTP, supports Modern Authentication (OAuth 2.0), and is not affected by Exchange Online limitations.

Otomatik Temizlik: Script başarıyla çalıştıktan sonra paylaşılan klasördeki CSV dosyalarını otomatik olarak siler. Bu sayede disk doluluğu ve veri karmaşası önlenir. 
Automated Cleanup: Automatically deletes CSV files in the shared folder after a successful run to prevent disk bloat and data clutter.

Hata Giderme (Escape Characters): Değişken tanımlamalarında ${id} kullanımı tercih edilerek PowerShell'in sürücü (Drive) belirteci hataları önlenmiştir.
Troubleshooting: The use of ${id} prevents PowerShell from misinterpreting the colon as a drive provider.


